                    "text": "The “Three Wheeler with Ice Box Including E-rickshaws for Fish Vending” is a scheme component under the Pradhan Mantri Matsya Sampada Yojana (PMMSY), implemented by the Fisheries Department, Government of Haryana. This is a Centrally Sponsored Scheme that aims to strengthen fish transportation infrastructure by promoting hygienic and efficient fish transportation and retailing through mobile outlets. Under this scheme, financial assistance is provided to eligible beneficiaries for purchasing e-rickshaws equipped with ice boxes for direct fish selling."
