      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a resident of Haryana.\n   1. The applicant should have a Parivar Pehchan Patra.\n   1. The applicant should ensure that the fish transport facility (e-rickshaw) is maintained in working condition.\n   1. The applicant is eligible to purchase only one new three-wheeler e-rickshaw with an ice box for fisheries activities under this scheme.\n   1. The applicant should agree that neither the Central Government nor the State Government shall be held responsible for any financial or operational losses incurred in the procurement, operation, maintenance, or management of the fish transport facilities.\n\n<br>\n\n",
